<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c2">(٢١)</span> ... <span class="c3">{طَهُورًا}</span> ... لَا رِجْسَ فِيهِ، وَلَا دَنَسَ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(٢٢)</span> ... <span class="c3">{سَعْيُكُم}</span> ... عَمَلُكُمُ الصَّالِحُ فِي الدُّنْيَا.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(٢٤)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لِحُكْمِ رَبِّكَ}</span> ... لِأَمْرِهِ القَدَرِيِّ فَتَقْبَلُهُ، وَلَأَمْرِهِ الشَّرْعِيِّ فَتَمْضِي عَلَيْهِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٢٥)</span> ... <span class="c3">{بُكْرَةً وَأَصِيلًا}</span> ... أَوَّلَ النَّهَارِ، وَآخِرَهُ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٢٦)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَسَبِّحْهُ}</span> ... صَلِّ لَهُ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٢٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَشَدَدْنَا أَسْرَهُمْ}</span> ... أَحْكَمْنَا خَلْقَهُمْ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٢٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{تَذْكِرَةٌ}</span> ... عِظَةٌ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c2">(٢٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{سَبِيلًا}</span> ... طَرِيقًا إِلَى اللهِ بِطَاعَتِهِ.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>